# 4-team rugby round-robin → top 2 advance to a knockout final
new-tournament SixNations rugby
add-stage round-robin Group 2
add-stage knockout Final
register Alpha
register Bravo
register Charlie
register Delta
close-registration
publish
start-tournament

# Round-robin: home wins by a try in every match
start-match next
action try home 10
finish-period
finish-period

start-match next
action try home 10
finish-period
finish-period

start-match next
action try home 10
finish-period
finish-period

start-match next
action try home 10
finish-period
finish-period

start-match next
action try home 10
finish-period
finish-period

start-match next
action try home 10
finish-period
finish-period

advance-stage
show standings

# Knockout final
start-match next
action try home 10
action conversion home 11
finish-period
finish-period
advance-stage
show winner
quit
